                <p>"Best school in Leyton! My instructor was so patient and really knew the Wanstead test routes."</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary);">— Local Student</p>
            </div>
            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="stars"><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
                <p>"Passed first time with only 2 minors. The safety-first approach really made me feel confident."</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary);">— Hackney Resident</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PRICING -->
    <section class="pricing" id="pricing">
        <h2>POPULAR LEARNER PACKAGES</h2>
        <div class="pricing-grid">
            <div class="price-card">
                <h3>Single Lesson</h3>
                <p>Standard hourly rate</p>
                <div class="cost">£38</div>
                <ul class="price-list">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 1-to-1 Tuition</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Door-to-door Pickup</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Manual or Automatic</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="https://wa.me/02085398888" class="btn btn-dark" style="width: 100%;">ENQUIRE NOW</a>
            </div>
            <div class="price-card featured">
                <h3>10 Hour Block</h3>
                <p>Save with Block Bookings</p>
                <div class="cost">£360</div>
                <ul class="price-list">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Discounted Rate</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Priority Slot Booking</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Full Progress Tracker</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="https://wa.me/02085398888" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">BOOK BLOCK</a>
            </div>
            <div class="price-card">
                <h3>Intensive Week</h3>
                <p>Fast Pass Specialist</p>
                <div class="cost">£750</div>
                <ul class="price-list">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 20 Hours of Tuition</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Mock Test Included</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <b>£10 NHS Discount</b></li>
                </ul>
                <a href="https://wa.me/02085398888" class="btn btn-dark" style="width: 100%;">GET STARTED</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- AREAS -->
    <section class="areas" id="areas">
        <div data-aos="fade-right">
            <h2 style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">EAST LONDON COVERAGE</h2>
            <p>We are experts in navigating the complex roads of London. We cover the following boroughs and test centers:</p>
            <div class="area-list">
                <div class="area-item">LEYTON (E10)</div>
                <div class="area-item">WALTHAMSTOW (E17)</div>
                <div class="area-item">CHINGFORD (E4)</div>
                <div class="area-item">HACKNEY</div>
                <div class="area-item">ILFORD</div>
                <div class="area-item">WANSTEAD</div>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 25px; font-weight: 600;"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Main Test Centers: Wanstead, Chingford, Loughton.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: var(--light); height: 350px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 4px solid var(--dark); border-radius: 20px;">
            <i class="fas fa-road fa-5x" style="color: var(--primary);"></i>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="faq">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">FREQUENT QUESTIONS</h2>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">Which areas do you cover? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div>
            <div class="accordion-content"><p style="padding: 20px;">We cover Leyton, Hackney, Chingford, Ilford, Walthamstow, and surrounding East London postcodes.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">Do you have female instructors? <i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div>
